window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Ominous Obelisks land on Earth with a single message:</b></p> <p>Join the Games to give humanity a fighting chance to survive... Or roll over and die.</p> <p>Too bad for them, Warren isn't the rolling over type.</p> <p>Warren is on the Battle World and, in order to survive, he needs to summon his inner diplomat.</p> <p>Warren is no diplomat.</p> <p>But despite lacking a mouth filter, he's forming very unlikely allies.</p> <p>Will they last? Or is Warren just setting himself (and humanity) up for a knife in the back?</p> <p><i>Perfect for fans of </i>Defiance of the Fall<i>, </i>Life in Exile<i>, and </i>Apocalypse: Generic System.</p> <p><i>Obelisk System Integration is an epic LitRPG Apocalypse series. This action-packed LitRPG/Progression series has our heroes facing off against an alien invasion, academy politics, PvP, and tower ascension, all to save Earth from being destroyed.</i></p>"; 
